name: Experiment Or Die #44
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. While listening to Dalek speak today in spaces I had a revelation to use yesterdays mint as the base for todays design instead of going all the way back to a blank canvas... so you can see very small portions of yesterdays layout throughout. I think for tomorrow I'll be sure to incorporate more of the existing design. You really need to search for those pieces peeking through. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
